      "title": "Book Thirty-Two: The Messiah Jesus Son of Mary (al-Masīḥ ‘Ῑsā Ibn Maryam): Herald of the Deuteronomy Prophet of the End of Days",
      "description": "Although Western calendars are dated from the Nativity of Jesus Christ, his actual year of birth was most likely 7 BCE, 6 BCE, or 4 BCE, with 4 BCE usually being preferred among Historians. If indeed 4 BCE is correct, then 1416/1996—not…",
